// These are derived values recomputed from legs array on each render.
// If legs hasn't changed, the component still re-renders if any OTHER
// subscribed property changes \(like itineraryName or settings\).
// These recomputations \(reduce over legs\) are O\(n\) but n is max 49 legs - trivial.
